    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>激烈的空战</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶攻击直升机参与快节奏战斗。结合精准射击与战术机动，应对外星威胁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/7136531200aea655ff987346ed8aed13.poster.avif?t=1771642031\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/7136531200aea655ff987346ed8aed13.webm?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/7136531200aea655ff987346ed8aed13.mp4?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>生态环境与战役</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索多样化的场景，并完成充满任务的章节。每个环境都有独特挑战，并以史诗级 Boss 战收尾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/bd90de045edb8efd80cc332ab5678be4.poster.avif?t=1771642031\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/bd90de045edb8efd80cc332ab5678be4.webm?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/bd90de045edb8efd80cc332ab5678be4.mp4?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>直升机进化</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集外星文物解锁升级和新型号。将你的直升机改造成装备先进外星科技的致命战斗机器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/af9077cd5c5fa9096480182a2468dfa4.poster.avif?t=1771642031\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/af9077cd5c5fa9096480182a2468dfa4.webm?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/af9077cd5c5fa9096480182a2468dfa4.mp4?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情与角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结识引导你完成任务的盟友，同时揭示入侵背后的秘密。剧情将动作、悬疑与神秘元素融合，带来沉浸式体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/3c7e36a8d85dc0ce89fd1b3a071a9ec1.poster.avif?t=1771642031\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/3c7e36a8d85dc0ce89fd1b3a071a9ec1.webm?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303890/extras/3c7e36a8d85dc0ce89fd1b3a071a9ec1.mp4?t=1771642031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
